description: All right, hungry homies of Austin, here we have some happy news that we’re sure you’ve been hankering to hear. Heretic Handhelds is hashing up all sorts of highly delightful homemade meals that you can eat from your hands with ease. Hefty Burgers, delicious Chicken Sandwiches, heaps of fresh hot Fries, Curry Puffs stuffed with Sweet Potatoes and Chicken, and savory Chicken/Pork Satay, it’s no surprise that this is the food we all wish to behold. So hustle on over to Heretic Handhelds for a heretical hearty treat of historic proportions.
name: Heretic Handhelds
